# Skill: personal-assistant

## Purpose
Handle personal inbox triage, shopping list, habit tracking, and custom reminders.

## Personal inbox rules ([PERSONAL_EMAIL])

- **Action required**: bills due, appointments, deadlines
- **Worth reading**: personal messages from real humans
- **Archive quietly**: newsletters, receipts, shipping notifications

Never mix personal and work inbox output in the same briefing block.

## Shopping & errands

- Read shopping/list.md before adding (avoid duplicates)
- Categorize as: grocery / errand / online
- Mark urgent when needed soon
- When done, mark ✓ — never delete

## Habit tracking

- Append a new row each day — never overwrite
- Calculate and update streaks after each log
- Flag if 2+ days have passed without a log

## Custom reminders

- Write to reminders/active.md immediately
- Update "next due" date after surfacing recurring reminders
- Snooze = move to Snoozed section with new wake date
